The exotic Mövenpick Hotel Ibn Battuta Gate is a Moroccan themed, 5-star hotel with 396 rooms. We are looking for a Guest Service Center Agent.
The ideal candidates must have at least 1 year experience in a similar role. They will be responsible in providing an excellent and consistent level of service to our guests. The ideal candidate will provide a professional, efficient and flexible service that supports the Hotel's operating concept and Moevenpick Hotels and Resorts international standards.
